{
  "stem": "19055.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 266.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That was after a bad winter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it was cold and-- and snowing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "By that time, it was April.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Spring didn't bring any beauty to this place, I must tell you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I still don't remember the sunshine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "All I remember that the snow was melting, and everything was dirty and filthy, and-- and the conditions were not good.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They were worse.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "There were more corpses, and more people died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And eventually, they stood us up and they said, we're going to leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So we marched out from Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We marched again to the railroad station and they placed us in a boxcars in a long train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we were not told anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We didn't know anything about the destination.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But as we learned later, we were taken south-- southeast from Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The journey began on the train again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And this train and the-- and the-- and the-- the rattling of the rails, it's still in my ears.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It-- it somehow, these train-- the journeys in the trains and the cattle cars made-- made-- made a terrible impression on me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Because every time we were in them, they always took us to something worse.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Every time the train left, I knew that it's something worse will come, and maybe ends in death.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day, we were going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The train was going and stopping, faster and slower.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The SS was with us everywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The SS were sitting in regular passenger cars, and we were in cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got sicker and sicker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I had fever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, if I would say, I probably had 104 temperature, with shaking, chills, and coughing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I begin to have pains in my chest and both sides, stabbing pains.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
